  "body": "Hi,\n\ni am trying to achieve a setup where prometheus stores long-term data in an InfluxDB or something. I know about the CLI flags `-storage.remote.influxdb-url`, `-storage.remote.influxdb.database` and `-storage.remote.influxdb.username`, since they show up in the `-h` output. But where should one specify the password of the influxdb user?\nEither it isn't implemented, or the -h output is incomplete, so i'm opening this issue. \n\nThanks.\n",
